snippet.title: NES Longplay [484] Wild Gunman
snippet.description:
http://www.longplays.org

Played by: Yushira

An NES Zapper game where the object of the game is to shoot the other guy within the alloted time before he shoots you. I go through all three modes to sample them. The game is endless. -
